{"tid":1307738,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[連儂牆]法國黃背心運動的 8 堂課:不死守任何公共空間","createTime":"2019-07-11T16:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T16:45:52.000Z","uid":12599,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a46443d8b1969e981b715a9406fccfe81439d8","tid":1307738,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:35:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/#.XQMbp-57BeV.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2Flessons-from-the-yellow-vests%2F%23.XQMbp-57BeV.facebook&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjviPq%2FHqG0pMUyXzarzxqBM%3D&h=04742083\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/#.XQMbp-57BeV.facebook</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不死守任何公共空間</span></span></strong><br />\n近年全球各地都流行佔領公共空間運動，縱然有助團結抗爭者，令其有平台公開表達訴求，但佔領運動始終有其缺點，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">一味據守陣地會虛耗資源和精力，民氣隨時間消耗，又更容易成為鎮壓目標。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n黃背心示威者反其道而行，不死守任何公共空間，在每個星期六湧上街頭，沒有任何既定路線，不預先公佈時間下快閃式堵路，用各種直接行動撼動政權。譬如堵塞高速公路和迴旋處，接管或燒毀道路收費站，讓汽車自由通行，令政府無利可圖。<br />\n<br />\n************************************************************<br />\n當初會打得咁好, 係因為唔再玩固守轉左去遊擊<br />\n<br />\n而家為左一幅連儂牆係咁俾人打, 又玩群眾鬥群眾, 原本五大訴求呢?又來雨傘2.0?<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆俾人拆完可以再起, 和理膠唔好再淨係識拍片影相跟住睇住d手足俾人打, 你地乜都唔做都係幫凶之一, 之後仲要俾個犯走甩到, 呢個行為真係比打人更可恥"},{"pid":"ac9f3612e269d8240243e6ebe86f0deda66a78da","tid":1307738,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa12b85b9ffc29e23bd23f0202ec176ecb0561d","tid":1307738